# {{context|music|lang=en}} In a piano or dulcimer, a piece of wood covered in felt that strikes the string.
# {{context|sports|lang=en}} A device made of a [[heavy]] steel [[ball]] attached to a length of [[wire]], and used for [[throw]]ing.
# {{context|curling|lang=en}} The last [[rock]] in an [[end]].
# {{context|Ultimate Frisbee|lang=en}} A frisbee throwing style in which the disc is held upside-down with a forehand grip and thrown above the head.
# Part of a [[clock]] that strikes upon a [[bell]] to indicate the [[hour]].
